(27, 1, '2015-05-04 10:36:34', '2015-05-04 10:36:34', '<div id="hiring" class="desc">\r\n<h2 class="full-w"><strong>We’re Hiring!</strong></h2>\r\n<p class="full-w">Social Voucher is a mobile application development company with a retail soul. Propelled by proprietary patent pending technology, a unique approach to social media and recommendations, and some of the most talented people on earth, we are positioned to transform global shopping.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class="full-w">Many have said we are changing the way people shop. We like to think of it as changing the game.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class="full-w">Join our team as we revolutionize e-commerce and have a ton of fun along the way. <a class="orange-col" href="mailto:jobs@socialvoucher.com"><strong>Send us</strong></a> your resume and any examples where you’ve changed the game.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class="full-w">Here are some of our open positions:</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="accordian full-w">\r\n<span class="<img src="http://localhost/socialvoucherdev/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/right-a.png" alt="right-a" width="32" height="32" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-26" />"></span>\r\n<h3><strong>Mobile and Web UX Designer</strong> <em>(Delray Beach, Flordia)</em></h3>\r\n<div class="details">\r\n\r\nThis position is for LOCAL residents only. Must be able to meet in our offices regularly.\r\n\r\nLooking for an exceptionally talented designer who has the skill not only to create high quality graphics, but the ability to apply their creations to user-centered design.\r\n\r\nA strong graphic designer portfolio is a good start, but we''re looking for more than just experience.\r\n\r\nExcellent html5, css3 and Drupal 7 knowledge, and the ability to position and control UI elements are necessary, along with an understanding of how to construct designs flexible enough to display across multiple browsers, screen sizes, platforms and devices.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a designer that will be able to understand how the users will want to instinctively interact with the UI, and provide them with the ability to perform their tasks intuitively.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>Responsibilities:</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Part of a design process involving research, experimentation, and revision.</li>\r\n	<li>Elicit constructive feedback and capable of interpreting that feedback into design solutions.</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborate with others and work well with developers and product management.</li>\r\n	<li>Familiar with Agile/Scrum methodology.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>Qualifications:</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ability to solve all sorts of design challenges with creativity, efficiency and precision; a full stack designer (interaction, usability, graphic design, html, css).</li>\r\n	<li>UI and UX Design expertise.</li>\r\n	<li>Skilled at building original web sites and applications focused on user experience.</li>\r\n	<li>Demonstrated custom web design skills.</li>\r\n	<li>Must be self-directed, confident and able to work in a fast-paced environment.</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent communication, both written and spoken English.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>Desirable Skills:</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Relevant undergraduate degree or 3-4 years of web and user application design experience.</li>\r\n	<li>Able to integrate UX into Agile development practices</li>\r\n	<li>Strong visual design skills: Latest trends, color and typography.</li>\r\n	<li>Strong interaction design skills: wireframing, prototyping, HTML5, CSS3.</li>\r\n	<li>A passion for semantic markup and standards.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with: iOS design, Android design</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><strong>Senior Unity 3D Designer</strong> <em>(Delray Beach, Flordia)</em></h3>\r\n<div class="details">\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a candidate that knows Unity 3D inside and out, from C# coding to backend integration. Ideal candidate has worked on numerous shipped game projects. You will be working on a breakthrough project with a talented and motivated team.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Responsibilities:</strong>\r\nIntegrate 2D and 3D assets into unity for use in a cross platform massively multiplayer online experience (MMO), develop and optimize in game processes, graphics, and\r\n<ul>Required Skills:</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Two or more years of professional Unity experience</li>\r\n	<li>Shipped at least 2 games</li>\r\n	<li>Mad C# skills</li>\r\n	<li>A passion for learning new things</li>\r\n	<li>A bachelor’s degree in CS or a related field</li>\r\n	<li>Android and iOS experience is a big bonus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><strong>Principle Engineer</strong> <em>(Delray Beach, Flordia)</em></h3>\r\n<div class="details">\r\n\r\nOur principal engineer is the keystone of our development team. The initial mission is to centralize all our development efforts in our facility in Florida and fully master any technical aspects of our product. In our development team, the principal engineer provides expertise and leads all technical software development.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>Requirements</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Software development master education</li>\r\n	<li>At least 10 years of experiences in software development</li>\r\n	<li>At least 5 years of experiences in mobile game development</li>\r\n	<li>Architecture Development</li>\r\n	<li>Experiences with iOS/Android development</li>\r\n	<li>Experiences with iOS/Android code signing and deployment</li>\r\n	<li>Experiences with Unity3D</li>\r\n	<li>Experiences with Scrum development</li>\r\n	<li>Strong knowledge in database and SQL</li>\r\n	<li>Strong knowledge in Web services (SOAP and Restful)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>Responsibilities</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Study customer’s requirements and framework, create design and code</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain and develop mobile applications</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain and develop web applications</li>\r\n	<li>Provide technical direction and feedback</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>Technical Skills</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>iOS/Android</li>\r\n	<li>Unity3D</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Big Data\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Google Cloud  Platform Architecture</li>\r\n	<li>AWS cloud architecture</li>\r\n	<li>User tracking</li>\r\n	<li>AB testing</li>\r\n	<li>DB cloud system (MONGO DB, Google Storage)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Language\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>C#</li>\r\n	<li>JS</li>\r\n	<li>Java/C</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Software development tools\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Atlasssian (JIRA/Confluence)</li>\r\n	<li>Git</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Software development methods\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Agile Scrum</li>\r\n	<li>Agile Kanban</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><strong>Hands-On Director of Marketing</strong> <em>(Delray Beach, Flordia)</em></h3>\r\n<div class="details">\r\n\r\nSocial Voucher is hiring a Director of Marketing out of our DelRay Beach Office. The ideal candidate will be responsible for managing and executing strategic integrated marketing programs and campaigns to grow brand awareness and drive customer acquisition &amp; retention. This position is hands-on and requires experience in launching and marketing mass market mobile applications and e-commerce platforms including user acquisition and retention strategies and tactics, blogger &amp; media relations, social media engagement, app store promotion and other digital and traditional marketing activities to create, grow and maintain a strong user base.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>The ideal candidate has:</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>At least 5 years hands-on experience in marketing a consumer tech offering, ideally including mobile applications and e-commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Experience building and engaging with a community of users including early-stage testers and early adopters via direct communication and social media</li>\r\n	<li>High motivation and is an avid user of mobile applications, very active within various social media environments and has experience working with online influencers including bloggers, and other media</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis is a great career opportunity with a lot of growth potential for the right candidate.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Careers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-04 10:36:34', '2015-05-04 10:36:34', '', 16, 'http://localhost/socialvoucherdev/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
