d develop mobile applications</li>\r\n	<li>Maintain and develop web applications</li>\r\n	<li>Provide technical direction and feedback</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><ul>Technical Skills</ul></strong>\r\n<br />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobile\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>iOS/Android</li>\r\n	<li>Unity3D</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Big Data\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Google Cloud  Platform Architecture</li>\r\n	<li>AWS cloud architecture</li>\r\n	<li>User tracking</li>\r\n	<li>AB testing</li>\r\n	<li>DB cloud system (MONGO DB, Google Storage)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Language\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>C#</li>\r\n	<li>JS</li>\r\n	<li>Java/C</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Software development tools\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Atlasssian (JIRA/Confluence)</li>\r\n	<li>Git</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Software development methods\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Agile Scrum</li>\r\n	<li>Agile Kanban</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><strong>Hands-On Director of Marketing</strong> <em>(Delray Beach, Flordia)</em><span class="right"></span></h3>\r\n<div class="details">\r\n<br />\r\nSocial Voucher is hiring a Director of Marketing out of our DelRay Beach Office. The ideal candidate will be responsible for managing and executing strategic integrated marketing programs and campaigns to grow brand awareness and drive customer acquisition &amp; retention. This position is hands-on and requires experience in launching and marketing mass market mobile applications and e-commerce platforms including user acquisition and retention strategies and tactics, blogger &amp; media relations, social media engagement, app store promotion and other digital and traditional marketing activities to create, grow and maintain a strong user base.\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<strong>The ideal candidate has:</strong>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>At least 5 years hands-on experience in marketing a consumer tech offering, ideally including mobile applications and e-commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Experience building and engaging with a community of users in